data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after Cherrywood Estates community! This exceptional property offers a unique opportunity to live in one of the most desirable neighborhoods, just minutes away from shopping, dining, and entertainment options.    One of the rare finds in this subdivision, this home boasts 4 bedrooms, a feature that sets it apart from the rest. With a thoughtfully designed split floor plan, this residence provides an ideal layout for both privacy and togetherness. The generous 2,433 square feet of living space ensures that you'll have all the room you need to live comfortably and luxuriously.    A standout feature of this home is the presence of not one, but two master bedrooms. Whether you're accommodating extended family, guests, or simply desiring an extra level of comfort, these spacious master suites are sure to delight.    The attached 2-car garage offers both convenience and ample storage space, making life's logistics a breeze. As you step into the bright and airy living spaces, you'll appreciate the natural light that floods the rooms, creating a warm and inviting ambiance.    Cherrywood Estates is a community renowned for its charm and convenient location. Imagine enjoying the tranquility of your peaceful home while still being within easy reach of all the amenities you could desire. The proximity to shopping, dining, and entertainment means that you'll always have something exciting to do just around the corner.    Call your Realtor today
